Definition: a member of a strictly orthodox Sunni Muslim sect from Saudi Arabia
Example: strives to purify Islamic beliefs and rejects any innovation occurring after the 3rd century of Islam; Osama bin Laden is said to be a Wahhabi Muslim
Synonyms: Wahabi, Muslim, a, member, of, strictly, orthodox, Sunni, sect, from, Saudi, Arabia, strives, to, purify, Islamic, beliefs, and, rejects, any, innovation, occurring, after, the, rd, century, Islam, Osama, bin, Laden, is, said, be
Category: noun.person
